'''Anthony Lang''' (d. [[March 2]], [[1992]])<ref name="Aveleyman" /> was the actor who portrayed [[Sim Aloo]] in [[Star Wars: Episode VI Return of the Jedi|''Star Wars'': Episode VI ''Return of the Jedi'']].<ref name="SWCA">{{SW|url=news/swca-secrets-of-the-mos-eisley-cantina-panel-liveblog|text=SWCA: Secrets of the Mos Eisley Cantina Panel Liveblog|nolive=1}}</ref> [[John Mollo]] also credits Anthony Lang as portraying one of four "local ugly men" in [[Star Wars: Episode IV A New Hope|''Star Wars'': Episode IV ''A New Hope'']] as documented in the [[1979]] book [[The Art of Star Wars Episode IV: A New Hope|''The Art of Star Wars'']].<ref name="TAoSW">[[The Art of Star Wars Episode IV: A New Hope|''The Art of Star Wars'']]</ref> According to [[Tom Spina]] and [[Pablo Hidalgo]], Lang also portrayed a [[Alliance to Restore the Republic|Rebel]] [[Technician]].<ref name="SWCA" />

